    "description": "<p>Pacific Prime is a leading global insurance advisor and global employee benefits specialist with over 500,000 clients worldwide. With 14 offices globally (Singapore, Hong Kong, Shanghai, Beijing, Dubai, Bangkok, Jakarta, Kuala Lumpur, Cebu, London, New York, Miami, Los Angeles, and Mexico City), we are able to offer a wide range of insurance solutions that transcend global and regional boundaries.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We have close to 500 employees globally, making us one of the largest intermediaries in Asia’s medical insurance and a leading distributor of International Medical Insurance plans. We arrange all types of insurance services worldwide with a diversified client base that includes both corporations and individuals.</p>",
